{"article_id":"1Iwu2AdX7Pmmv7R2","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"President Trump on Monday specifically condemned \" white supremacists \" and \" neo-Nazis \" in the wake of deadly weekend clashes in Charlottesville ,","depth":4},{"id":1,"text":"vowing","depth":5},{"id":2,"text":"\" justice will be delivered \" to the perpetrators of that `` racist violence . ''","depth":5},{"id":3,"text":"The president ,","depth":6},{"id":4,"text":"after meeting with Attorney General Jeff Sessions and FBI Director Christopher Wray in Washington ,","depth":6},{"id":5,"text":"said","depth":5},{"id":6,"text":"his Justice Department has opened a civil rights probe into the deadly car attack on Saturday .","depth":4},{"id":7,"text":"After facing bipartisan criticism for his initial statement over the weekend ,","depth":4},{"id":8,"text":"Trump was direct in his condemnation Monday .","depth":4},{"id":9,"text":"\" We condemn in the strongest possible terms this egregious display of hatred , bigotry and violence .","depth":6},{"id":10,"text":"It has no place in America , \"","depth":6},{"id":11,"text":"Trump said .","depth":5},{"id":12,"text":"He added ,","depth":5},{"id":13,"text":"\" Racism is evil ,","depth":6},{"id":14,"text":"and those","depth":8},{"id":15,"text":"who cause violence in its name","depth":8},{"id":16,"text":"are criminals and thugs ,","depth":8},{"id":17,"text":"including the KKK , neo-Nazis , white supremacists and other hate groups","depth":9},{"id":18,"text":"that are repugnant to everything","depth":10},{"id":19,"text":"we hold dear as Americans . \"","depth":10},{"id":20,"text":"The president 's remarks at the White House had not been anticipated .","depth":5},{"id":21,"text":"He is in Washington for a day of meetings and work ,","depth":6},{"id":22,"text":"interrupting his August vacation at his New Jersey golf club .","depth":6},{"id":23,"text":"But he delivered the prepared statement on the heels of criticism ,","depth":6},{"id":24,"text":"including from members of his own party ,","depth":6},{"id":25,"text":"for not speaking out specifically or forcefully enough at first against the white supremacist groups","depth":6},{"id":26,"text":"involved in Saturday 's clashes .","depth":6},{"id":27,"text":"The president on Saturday had condemned violence and hatred on \" many sides , \"","depth":6},{"id":28,"text":"but faced swift criticism","depth":7},{"id":29,"text":"as video emerged from the scene in Charlottesville","depth":8},{"id":30,"text":"showing a car","depth":9},{"id":31,"text":"ramming into a crowd of counter-protesters .","depth":9},{"id":32,"text":"One person died in that attack ;","depth":6},{"id":33,"text":"two state police also died in a chopper crash .","depth":6},{"id":34,"text":"Republican lawmakers joined Democrats","depth":5},{"id":35,"text":"in saying","depth":6},{"id":36,"text":"Trump should call out white supremacists directly .","depth":6},{"id":37,"text":"The president was again challenged , by a reporter , during a separate White House event later in the day Monday","depth":6},{"id":38,"text":"on why he did not condemn these hate groups from the start .","depth":6},{"id":39,"text":"\" They ' ve been condemned .","depth":7},{"id":40,"text":"They have been condemned , \"","depth":7},{"id":41,"text":"Trump said .","depth":6},{"id":42,"text":"When CNN ' s Jim Acosta asked","depth":6},{"id":43,"text":"if the press could ask more questions ,","depth":6},{"id":44,"text":"he responded ,","depth":6},{"id":45,"text":"\" I like real news , not fake news .","depth":7},{"id":46,"text":"You ' re fake news . \"","depth":7},{"id":47,"text":"His remarks Monday , however , could ease some of the outcry , at least from his own party .","depth":4},{"id":48,"text":"Trump said Monday","depth":6},{"id":49,"text":"that anyone","depth":8},{"id":50,"text":"who acted criminally","depth":8},{"id":51,"text":"will be held `` fully accountable . ''","depth":7},{"id":52,"text":"`` No matter the color of our skin ,","depth":7},{"id":53,"text":"we all live under the same laws ,","depth":8},{"id":54,"text":"we all salute the same great flag ,","depth":9},{"id":55,"text":"and we are all made by the same almighty God , ''","depth":9},{"id":56,"text":"Trump said .","depth":6}],"relations":[{"parent":113,"left":76,"right":112,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":76,"left":63,"right":75,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":63,"left":59,"right":62,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":59,"left":0,"right":58,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":58,"left":1,"right":2,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":62,"left":61,"right":6,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":61,"left":60,"right":5,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":60,"left":3,"right":4,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":75,"left":64,"right":74,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":64,"left":7,"right":8,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":74,"left":66,"right":73,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":66,"left":65,"right":11,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":65,"left":9,"right":10,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":73,"left":12,"right":72,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":72,"left":13,"right":71,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":71,"left":67,"right":70,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":67,"left":14,"right":15,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":70,"left":16,"right":69,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":69,"left":17,"right":68,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":68,"left":18,"right":19,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":112,"left":92,"right":111,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":92,"left":82,"right":91,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":82,"left":78,"right":81,"relation":"adversative","